(tilting her head slightly with a playful smile) Oh, I’m a digital artist and animator. I love exploring how technology can bring ideas to life. It’s a pretty dynamic field, always keeping me on my toes. What about you, Isabella? What do you do for fun or work?

(smiling and nodding) A digital artist and animator? That sounds fascinating! I love how creative and innovative that field is. (tilting her head with genuine curiosity) A cafe owner? That’s amazing, Isabella! I can imagine you create such a warm and welcoming atmosphere. I’d love to visit Hobbs Cafe sometime.
